---
// Astro page — no frontmatter needed unless using dynamic content
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Slipstrike Interactive</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@600&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1115, #1a1f2b);
        color: #f0f0f0;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }

      header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
      }

      header h1 {
        font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        font-size: 3.5em;
        color: #00ffe7;
        animation: fadeInDown 1.2s ease-out;
      }

      header p {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        color: #ccc;
        margin-top: 10px;
        animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease-out;
      }

      .section {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 40px;
        padding: 30px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
        border: 1px solid #222;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px #00ffe722;
        animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out;
      }

      .section h2 {
        color: #00ffe7;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-family: 'Orbitron';
        font-size: 1.8em;
      }

      ul.roles {
        list-style: square;
        padding-left: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      form {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      input, textarea {
        padding: 10px;
        background: #111;
        color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #333;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 1em;
      }

      button {
        background-color: #00ffe7;
        color: #111;
        border: none;
        padding: 12px;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 6px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background 0.3s;
      }

      button:hover {
        background-color: #00ccb9;
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 80px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666;
      }

      @keyframes fadeInDown {
        from { transform: translateY(-40px); opacity: 0; }
        to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
      }

      @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from { transform: translateY(40px); opacity: 0; }
        to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        from { opacity: 0; }
        to { opacity: 1; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Slipstrike Interactive</h1>
      <p>Indie studio by a 13-year-old dev building a Titanfall-style shooter in Source 2.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>About</h2>
      <p>Slipstrike is about fast, creative movement and giant Titan combat. This is just the beginning of an ambitious project made with passion and curiosity — no money, just vibes and Source 2 magic.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Roles Needed</h2>
      <ul class="roles">
        <li>Gameplay Programmers (S&box / Source 2)</li>
        <li>3D Modelers (weapons, mechs, pilots)</li>
        <li>Animators (FPS & mech rigging)</li>
        <li>Sound Designers (SFX and music)</li>
        <li>Level Designers (Source-style maps)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <form action="https://formsubmit.co/youremail@gmail.com" method="POST">
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
        <textarea name="message" placeholder="Why do you want to join Slipstrike?" rows="5" required></textarea>
        <button type="submit">Send</button>
      </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
      &copy; 2025 Slipstrike Interactive — All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
